org.sd.classifier
Class ArffVisitor

java.lang.Object
  org.sd.classifier.ArffVisitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
ArffTranslator
public abstract class ArffVisitor
extends java.lang.Object

Base utility for visiting the attributes and instances in an arff.

This class is thread safe (at this level).

Author:
Spence Koehler

visitFeatureVector

protected abstract boolean visitFeatureVector(FeatureDictionary featureDictionary,
                                              java.util.List<FeatureAttribute> featureAttributes,
                                              java.lang.String instanceLine,

Visit the given feature vector's instance line.

An implementation can call the visitVectorValues method and override the visitVectorValue method.

Returns:
true to keep iterating, false to stop iterating over attributes.

visitVectorValues

protected final boolean visitVectorValues(FeatureDictionary featureDictionary,
                                          java.util.List<FeatureAttribute> featureAttributes,
                                          java.lang.String instanceLine,
                                          int instanceNum)
Utility method to call to visit each value in a vector instance.

Override the visitVectorValue method to handle each value.

Returns:
true if all values were visited; otherwise, false.
